README: This task requires participants to make choices either for themselves or for other individuals in the study between a larger amount of money later or a smaller amount of money sooner. Participants were matched with those with dissimilar preferences. Agent refers to decision-making for Self (0) or Other (1). Delay is the delay to receiving reward in days. Money is the potential reward in USD.
